title: Greenaway - A Zed & Two Noughts - 1985
description:
<a href="http://imdb.com/title/tt0090366/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://imdb.com/title/tt0090366/</a>

My favorite Peter Greenaway film.  Decay, and more decay.  Lovely typographical references to his older movies, and a couple of pairs of nice underwear. Amputee fetishism.  Zebra fetishism.  Fetishism...

Killer Michael Nyman score.

Comes with some interesting extras (some are hidden).
